text: Novopreobrazhensky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Zilairsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Zilair. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Novopreobrazhensky
